	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64768856">Make grades mean something, stop worrying about parent's feelings.
<br> <br>
If your child is dumb wouldn't you rather know it now? You can better help them plan a future while making your own efforts knowledgeable with less waste.
<br> <br>
If your child is smarter you would absolutely want to know it now. This no child left behind crap assumes a level playing field. It isn't, some are smart; some are less so; and everyone else is in between.</div>
	</div>

