	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64768872"><p>The reviews and scores that a student gives to a professor in a particular class are very strongly correlated to the grade that they receive.  So, it's no surprise that professors who wish to receive teaching awards and the accompanying compensation and recognition will inflate the grade they give to students.</p></div>
