		<div id="comment_body_64768946">Kids there are super hardworking and smart.  Most of them actually do deserve As and Bs.  If average GPA in these schools are 2.6 then it'll hurt these kids applying for grad schools.   Having been to tier-1 myself, just being able to pass the classes are already way harder than less selective schools.

